Sept./Oct. 1987.
[16]   R. Lessmeier, W.
Schumacher, and W. Leonhard, “Microprocessor-controlled ac-servo drives with
synchronous or induction motors: which is preferable ?,” IEEE Trans. on Ind. Appl., vol. 22, no. 5, pp. 812-819, Sep./Oct.
1986.
[17]   M. A. Rahman,
“Permanent magnet synchronous motors - a review of the state of design art,” Proc. Intl. Conference on Electrical
Machines, Athens, pp. 312-319, 1980.
[18]   P. Pillay, B. K.
Bose, et al., Performance and Design of Permanent Magnet AC Motor Drives, Tutorial Course of the IEEE Industry
Applications Society Annual Meeting, Dearborn, Michigan, 1991.
